Halt! Who go there? Who
challenge Ryuuryuu?

rows.label: tlk70000024_01_msg0002
rows.name:
Strangers come here to kick
us out? Old lady from market
must have told on us again!

rows.label: tlk70000024_01_msg0003
rows.name:
Mo! Ryuuryuu and brotherpons find
this tip-top base! Is ours!

rows.label: tlk70000024_01_msg0004
rows.name:
If friends want us to move, friends
find better base for us, hm?
